creator: I AM PART OF
descriptionHtml:
Divine uses space technologies to transmit the Holy Quran from a satellite.

Divine is carried to an orbit by a “Falcon 9 Space X” rocket in partnership with “SpaceChain”.

• Divine uses space technologies to broadcast the teaching of Islam and the Holy Quran around the world.

• Divine offers you a collection of Dua, Ayat of the Day and access to the Holy Quran teachings.

• Divine offers you a complete tutorial on how to perform a Salah.

• Divine is part of the Global Charity Fund “IamPartOf.org” and offers you an opportunity to donate Zakat to the people in need around the world.

• Divine supports different languages, including English and Russian.
